{"tid":2291471,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"以色列報復敘利亞 空襲炸死10名戰士","createTime":"2020-11-18T21:36:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-19T15:23:52.000Z","uid":295230,"like":65,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"713d38a72e05364814aa03d5086e477907f3b1b9","tid":2291471,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T21:36:39.000Z","msg":"以色列今天空襲敘利亞，造成10人死亡，包括3位敘利亞防空部隊人員與7名外籍戰士。<br />\n<br />\n法新社報導，總部在英國的敘利亞人權瞭望台組織（Syrian Observatory for Human Rights）表示，喪生的7名外籍戰士有5人「可能是伊朗人，隸屬聖城部隊（Quds Force）」，另有2名國籍不明的親伊朗戰士。<br />\n<br />\n敘利亞人權瞭望台組織負責人阿布杜拉曼（Rami Abdel Rahman）指出，此次的空襲鎖定2個防空陣地為目標，分別位在敘利亞首都大馬士革機場附近與大馬士革西南方。<br />\n<br />\n阿布杜拉曼表示，其他目標包括大馬士革南方親伊朗武裝分子使用的陣地和彈藥庫，包括薩伊達宰那布（Sayyeda Zeinab）和基斯威（Kisweh）附近陣地。<br />\n<br />\n以色列軍方表示，昨天在以色列所佔領戈蘭高地（Golan Heights）的一處基地附近發現爆炸裝置，因此清晨展開報復空襲。<br />\n<br />\n自2011年敘利亞爆發內戰以來，以色列已對敘利亞發動數百次空襲與飛彈攻擊，目標是伊朗、黎巴嫩真主黨（Lebanese Hezbollah）與政府軍部隊。"},{"pid":"5477db515d413be503784da3fb6ee2f55fb2edd9","tid":2291471,"uid":295230,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T21:36:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202011180327.aspx?fbclid=IwAR04b7gPQeEcoeB4eo6cFSQW4cNsChFZedXGmThdw-HjROT-Tl_FfsSDTu8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Ffirstnews%2F202011180327.aspx%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR04b7gPQeEcoeB4eo6cFSQW4cNsChFZedXGmThdw-HjROT-Tl_FfsSDTu8&d=VbAd486K8RrC2DEUtq3b5u2wegjmRFMzjbv%2B285MJ7g%3D&h=98f45318\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202011180327.aspx?fbclid=IwAR04b7gPQeEcoeB4eo6cFSQW4cNsChFZedXGmThdw-HjROT-Tl_FfsSDTu8</a>"},{"pid":"4b99cb94e42083a091dfd78a075923afa78e0288","tid":2291471,"uid":290404,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T22:59:59.000Z","msg":"以色列做得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8e581a6084f9cd3b7212cd5866513cde4b59568","tid":2291471,"uid":30040,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"202